d HYPER-V cluster in our NL facility and proud to offer reliable Windows hosts. Check it out now!','2015-06-09 00:00:00',NULL,0),(48,'NEW Windows VPS (RDP) in NL from 7 EUR only!','HOSTKEY finally deployed HYPER-V cluster in our NL facility and proud to offer reliable Windows hosts. Check it out now!','2015-06-09 00:00:00',NULL,0),(49,'NEW Windows VPS (RDP) in NL from 7 EUR only!','HOSTKEY finally deployed HYPER-V cluster in our NL facility and proud to offer reliable Windows hosts. Check it out now!','2015-06-09 00:00:00',NULL,0),(50,'Самая свежая новость с заголовком','Описаниме \r\n\"Самая свежая новость с заголовком\"','2015-06-30 00:00:00','<p class=\"b-news-one__item-text\">We would like to inform you that the European Directive 2002/38/EC has introduced new VAT rules involving business to consumer supplies of digital services, which came into force on the 1st January 2015.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"b-news-one__item-text\">According to the new rules, end customers will be liable for segmented VAT rates depending on the country of their own residency, not on the country where the provider is located (as it has been until now). This change may either decrease or increase your monthly charges for our services depending on your residency.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"b-news-one__item-text\">For example, our customer based in Germany (VAT 19%) will be paying less than a customer in the Netherlands (VAT 21%), because of the difference in the VAT policies of those two countries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"b-news-one__item-text\">This change is only applicable to all of our customers (new and existing) that are private individuals residing in the EU and EU based businesses that have not provided us with a valid EU VAT ID:</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"b-news-one__item-text\">This change does not affect: &ndash; Any customers based in the Netherlands; &ndash; Any EU business customers that have provided us with a valid EU VAT ID; &ndash; Any customers residing outside the EU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"b-news-one__item-text\">All of our customers who are affected by this change will have new invoices generated displaying the VAT rate of their member state. If you&rsquo;re paying your invoices using automatic subscription payments we kindly ask you to update (cancel current subscription and create subscription with an updated amount) them accordingly to avoid unwanted service suspension.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"b-news-one__item-text\">We kindly ask you to make sure you have your address details correct in profile so that the correct VAT can be calculated: this is the law. If you require any assistance, have questions or concerns, please contact our billing department with: <a class=\"b-link\" href=\"#\">bill@hostkey.com</a></p>',1),(51,'Amsterdam is getting closer','HOSTKEY is now directly connected to Amsterdam Internet Exchange (AMS-IX) as a full-fledged member.','2015-07-07 00:00:00','<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">HOSTKEY constantly strives to improve its services and the quality of global connectivity. That is why we are particularly proud to announce that HOSTKEY is now directly connected to <a href=\"https://ams-ix.net/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#945AE0;\"><b>Amsterdam Internet Exchange (AMS-IX)</b></span></a> as a full-fledged member.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">AMS-IX is a neutral Internet Exchange point situated in Amsterdam, the Netherlands. AMS-IX was founded in 1994 and is a fast-growing non-profit independent peering point. The AMS-IX is currently world&rsquo; second largest Internet Exchange with 700+ members. The business traffic has a peak of close to 4 Terabit per second.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">The link capacity between HOSTKEY&rsquo;s datacenter and AMS-IX is currently 10 Gbps and it will increase accordingly. This way the company has achieved a substantial channel capacity for its customers and partners around the world, who are in demand for high-quality &amp; fast connectivity.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Direct connection without using third-party links will allow HOSTKEY to significantly accelerate access to the servers located in the Dutch Datacenter for our worldwide users. It will also reduce the upstream connectivity costs for our clients. Other benefits include improved performance and redundancy of our network in the Netherlands and faster distribution of traffic across many networks.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">HOSTKEY is inviting providers participating AMS-IX to establish direct peering connections.</span></p>',1),(52,'One new number for all you needs and queries!','We are excited to announce that starting from today we have one number to reach all the departments: \r\n+31 20 820 3777','2015-07-09 00:00:00','<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">HOSTKEY always does its best to make the communication between the clients and our staff as easy and convenient as possible.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">That is why we are excited to announce that starting from today we have one number to reach all the departments: +31 20 820 3777.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Previously our clients had to dial different numbers depending on the department they wanted to reach. That is in the past now.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Unlike other companies, you are not going to be redirected to some remote call center. No! You will get through to our team of professionals who will do their best to assist you with your inquiry or issue.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Try it out for yourself!</span></p>',1);

